msgstr ""
"| 逻辑NPU映射 | `npu-smi info -m` | 将卡/芯片ID映射到全局逻辑NPU "
"ID，并给出`total_logic_npus`。在Ascend 950上，不报告`Chip Logic ID`，因此使用`NPU ID`作为逻辑ID。"
" |"

msgid ""
"| Running NPUs | `npu-smi info` process table, filtered by "
"`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES` | Identifies the logical NPUs used by this "
"worker process. A2/A3 process rows use `NPU Chip`; Ascend 950 process rows "
"use `NPU ID`. |"
msgstr ""
"| 运行中的NPU | `npu-smi info`进程表，经`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES`过滤 | "
"标识此工作进程使用的逻辑NPU。A2/A3进程行使用`NPU Chip`；Ascend 950进程行使用`NPU ID`。 |"

msgid ""
"| Topology affinity | `npu-smi info -t topo` | Provides NPU-to-CPU affinity "
"for `topo_affinity` mode. |"
msgstr ""
"| 拓扑亲和性 | `npu-smi info -t topo` | 为`topo_affinity`模式提供NPU到CPU的亲和性信息。 |"

msgid ""
"| CPU NUMA map | `lscpu -e=CPU,NODE` | Used to extend single-NUMA affinity "
"pools to the next NUMA node. |"
msgstr "| CPU NUMA映射 | `lscpu -e=CPU,NODE` | 用于将单NUMA亲和性池扩展到下一个NUMA节点。 |"

msgid ""
"| A3 | `global_slice` | A3 uses HCCS card-to-card interconnect. Each NPU is "
"nearly equidistant from all NUMA nodes, so there is no strong NPU-to-NUMA "
"affinity signal. Global logical NPU ID based slicing gives deterministic, "
"non-overlapping CPU pools and CPU/NUMA isolation between workers. |"
msgstr ""
"| A3 | `global_slice` | "
"A3使用HCCS卡间互联。每个NPU与所有NUMA节点的距离几乎相等，因此没有强烈的NPU到NUMA亲和性信号。基于全局逻辑NPU "
"ID的分片提供确定性的、不重叠的CPU池以及工作进程间的CPU/NUMA隔离。 |"

msgid ""
"| A2 and Atlas 300 inference products | `topo_affinity` | A2 and Atlas 300 "
"inference products provide NPU-to-CPU affinity information through `npu-smi "
"info -t topo`, so they use this topology signal when available. |"
msgstr ""
"| A2和Atlas 300推理产品 | `topo_affinity` | A2和Atlas 300推理产品通过`npu-smi info -t "
"topo`提供NPU到CPU的亲和性信息，因此在可用时会使用此拓扑信号。 |"

msgid "| SQ/CQ IRQ | `pool[0]`, `pool[1]` |"
msgstr "| SQ/CQ IRQ | `pool[0]`, `pool[1]` |"

msgid "| Main worker process and subthreads | `pool[2:-2]` |"
msgstr "| 主工作进程及子线程 | `pool[2:-2]` |"

msgid "| ACL thread | `pool[-2]` |"
msgstr "| ACL线程 | `pool[-2]` |"

msgid "| Release thread | `pool[-1]` |"
msgstr "| 释放线程 | `pool[-1]` |"

msgid ""
"| Thread topology | `lscpu` `Thread(s) per core` | Determines Ascend 950 "
"cluster size: 8 CPUs for 1 thread per core, 16 CPUs for 2 threads per core. "
"|"
msgstr ""
"| 线程拓扑 | `lscpu` `每个核心的线程数` | 决定 Ascend 950 集群大小：1 线程每核心时为 8 个 CPU，2 线程每核心时为"
" 16 个 CPU。 |"

msgid ""
"| UVB polling threads | `ps -Te` | Finds host `uvb_poll_window_thread` "
"threads for Ascend 950 UVB CPU binding. Docker containers must use "
"`--pid=host` to see these host threads. |"
msgstr ""
"| UVB 轮询线程 | `ps -Te` | 查找主机 `uvb_poll_window_thread` 线程以用于 Ascend 950 UVB "
"CPU 绑定。Docker 容器必须使用 `--pid=host` 才能看到这些主机线程。 |"

msgid ""
"| Ascend 950 | `topo_affinity` | Ascend 950 uses NPU-to-CPU affinity from "
"`npu-smi info -t topo` to choose an affinity NUMA node, then assigns one CPU"
" cluster from that NUMA node to each worker. It also reports process rows by"
" `NPU ID` instead of `NPU Chip`, skips IRQ binding, and binds host UVB "
"polling threads. |"
msgstr ""
"| Ascend 950 | `topo_affinity` | Ascend 950 使用来自 `npu-smi info -t topo` 的 "
"NPU 到 CPU 亲和性来选择亲和性 NUMA 节点，然后从该 NUMA 节点为每个工作进程分配一个 CPU 集群。它还按 `NPU ID` 而非 "
"`NPU Chip` 报告进程行，跳过 IRQ 绑定，并绑定主机 UVB 轮询线程。 |"

msgid ""
"`global_slice` is designed for devices without a useful NPU-to-CPU affinity\n"
"signal, including A3. Because A3's **HCCS interconnect makes the distance\n"
"from each NPU to each NUMA node nearly the same**, topology affinity is not a\n"
"useful placement signal. The allocator therefore partitions the sorted\n"
"`allowed_cpus` list by global logical NPU ID."
msgstr ""
"`global_slice` 专为没有有效 NPU 到 CPU 亲和性信号的设备设计，包括 A3。由于 A3 的 **HCCS 互连使得每个 NPU "
"到每个 NUMA 节点的距离几乎相同**，拓扑亲和性不是一个有用的放置信号。因此，分配器按全局逻辑 NPU ID 对排序后的 "
"`allowed_cpus` 列表进行分区。"

msgid ""
"- Devices with IRQ binding require `base >= 5`:\n"
"  2 CPUs for SQ/CQ IRQ binding, at least 1 CPU for the main worker, 1 CPU for\n"
"  ACL thread, and 1 CPU for release thread."
msgstr ""
"- 具有 IRQ 绑定的设备要求 `base >= 5`：\n"
"  2 个 CPU 用于 SQ/CQ IRQ 绑定，至少 1 个 CPU 用于主工作进程，1 个 CPU 用于 ACL 线程，以及 1 个 CPU 用于释放线程。"

msgid ""
"`topo_affinity` is designed for A2, Atlas 300 inference products, Ascend 950,\n"
"and other non-A3 device types. A2 and Atlas 300 inference products expose\n"
"**meaningful NPU-to-CPU affinity information**, so the allocator starts from NPU\n"
"topology affinity when it is available and then avoids overlap for shared\n"
"affinity groups."
msgstr ""
"`topo_affinity` 专为 A2、Atlas 300 推理产品、Ascend 950 和其他非 A3 设备类型设计。A2 和 Atlas "
"300 推理产品暴露了**有意义的 NPU 到 CPU 亲和性信息**，因此分配器在可用时从 NPU 拓扑亲和性开始，然后避免共享亲和性组的重叠。"

msgid "For Ascend 950, topology affinity is used differently:"
msgstr "对于 Ascend 950，拓扑亲和性的使用方式不同："

msgid ""
"1. Bind all visible host `uvb_poll_window_thread` threads to NUMA0 CPUs except CPU0, constrained by `allowed_cpus`. Docker containers must use `--pid=host` to make these host threads visible.\n"
"2. Use topo affinity to identify each NPU's single affinity NUMA node.\n"
"3. Parse `Thread(s) per core` from `lscpu` and set cluster size to 8 CPUs when it is 1, or 16 CPUs when it is 2.\n"
"4. Split each affinity NUMA's sorted allowed CPU list into contiguous clusters.\n"
"5. Assign clusters by sorted logical NPU ID, including hidden NPUs that share the same affinity NUMA.\n"
"6. Keep only running NPUs in the final `npu_cpu_pool`."
msgstr ""
"1. 将所有可见的主机 `uvb_poll_window_thread` 线程绑定到除 CPU0 之外的 NUMA0 CPU，受 `allowed_cpus` 约束。Docker 容器必须使用 `--pid=host` 才能使这些主机线程可见。\n"
"2. 使用拓扑亲和性来识别每个 NPU 的单个亲和性 NUMA 节点。\n"
"3. 从 `lscpu` 解析 `每个核心的线程数`，当值为 1 时将集群大小设置为 8 个 CPU，值为 2 时设置为 16 个 CPU。\n"
"4. 将每个亲和性 NUMA 的排序后的允许 CPU 列表分割成连续的集群。\n"
"5. 按排序后的逻辑 NPU ID 分配集群，包括共享相同亲和性 NUMA 的隐藏 NPU。\n"
"6. 在最终的 `npu_cpu_pool` 中仅保留正在运行的 NPU。"

msgid ""
"If Ascend 950 topo affinity is missing, spans multiple NUMA nodes, has too few\n"
"clusters, or reports an unsupported `Thread(s) per core`, worker CPU binding is\n"
"skipped without raising to the worker process."
msgstr ""
"如果 Ascend 950 的拓扑亲和性缺失、跨越多个 NUMA 节点、集群过少或报告了不支持的 `每个核心的线程数`，则工作进程 CPU "
"绑定将被跳过，不会向工作进程抛出异常。"

msgid "| Main worker process and subthreads | the whole assigned cluster |"
msgstr "| 主工作进程及子线程 | 整个分配的集群 |"

msgid "| ACL thread | not separately pinned |"
msgstr "| ACL 线程 | 不单独绑定 |"

msgid "| Release thread | not separately pinned |"
msgstr "| 释放线程 | 不单独绑定 |"

msgid ""
"If a final pool has fewer CPUs than the selected role split requires, binding\n"
"fails for this rank and the worker logs a warning from the caller. The minimum\n"
"is 5 CPUs per NPU for devices with IRQ binding. Ascend 950 requires one full\n"
"cluster per worker."
msgstr ""
"如果最终池中的 CPU 数量少于所选角色拆分所需的数量，则该 rank 的绑定失败，工作进程会从调用者处记录一条警告。对于具有 IRQ 绑定的设备，每个"
" NPU 至少需要 5 个 CPU。Ascend 950 要求每个工作进程有一个完整的集群。"

msgid ""
"- Memory migration uses `migratepages` to move the worker process's existing\n"
"  pages to the selected NUMA node. This keeps the worker closer to the memory it\n"
"  reads and reduces remote-NUMA memory read latency.\n"
"- IRQ binding places NPU IRQ handling on the CPUs reserved for the corresponding\n"
"  NPU when `/proc/irq` is writable and IRQ files can be resolved.\n"
"  Ascend 950 skips this step."
msgstr ""
"- 内存迁移使用 `migratepages` 将工作进程的现有页面移动到选定的 NUMA 节点。这使工作进程更接近其读取的内存，并减少远程 NUMA 内存读取延迟。\n"
"- 当 `/proc/irq` 可写且 IRQ 文件可解析时，IRQ 绑定将 NPU IRQ 处理放置在为相应 NPU 保留的 CPU 上。Ascend 950 跳过此步骤。"

msgid ""
"Ascend 950 uses a different role split, so its plan log does not include ACL or\n"
"release fields. UVB polling thread binding is reported separately when matching\n"
"threads are found:"
msgstr "Ascend 950 使用不同的角色拆分，因此其计划日志不包括 ACL 或释放字段。当找到匹配的线程时，UVB 轮询线程绑定会单独报告："

msgid ""
"- CPU binding runs only on ARM. It is skipped on x86_64.\n"
"- Each final NPU pool must have enough CPUs for its role split: at least 5 CPUs\n"
"  for devices with IRQ binding. Ascend 950 requires one complete CPU cluster per worker.\n"
"- `global_slice` is deterministic and provides CPU/NUMA isolation when the\n"
"  cpuset is NUMA-aligned, but it cannot guarantee NUMA-local pools when CPU\n"
"  numbering or cpuset layout crosses NUMA boundaries.\n"
"- `topo_affinity` depends on usable output from `npu-smi info -t topo`.\n"
"- IRQ binding requires writable `/proc/irq` and resolvable PCI/IRQ information.\n"
"  Ascend 950 skips IRQ binding even when `/proc/irq` is writable.\n"
"- Ascend 950 UVB polling thread binding requires visibility into the host PID\n"
"  namespace. Docker containers must be created with `--pid=host`; otherwise\n"
"  `uvb_poll_window_thread` may not be found.\n"
"- Memory migration requires `migratepages`; otherwise only memory migration is\n"
"  skipped. CPU affinity still applies, but performance may degrade because\n"
"  existing pages are not moved to the target NUMA node and may be read through\n"
"  higher-latency remote NUMA access.\n"
"- If an exception escapes the binding flow, `NPUWorker` logs a warning and skips CPU binding for that rank."
msgstr ""
"- CPU 绑定仅在 ARM 上运行。在 x86_64 上跳过。\n"
"- 每个最终的 NPU 池必须有足够的 CPU 用于其角色拆分：对于具有 IRQ 绑定的设备，至少需要 5 个 CPU。Ascend 950 要求每个工作进程有一个完整的 CPU 集群。\n"
"- `global_slice` 是确定性的，当 cpuset 与 NUMA 对齐时提供 CPU/NUMA 隔离，但当 CPU 编号或 cpuset 布局跨越 NUMA 边界时，它无法保证 NUMA 本地池。\n"
"- `topo_affinity` 依赖于 `npu-smi info -t topo` 的可用输出。\n"
"- IRQ 绑定需要可写的 `/proc/irq` 和可解析的 PCI/IRQ 信息。即使 `/proc/irq` 可写，Ascend 950 也会跳过 IRQ 绑定。\n"
"- Ascend 950 UVB 轮询线程绑定需要能够看到主机 PID 命名空间。Docker 容器必须使用 `--pid=host` 创建；否则可能找不到 `uvb_poll_window_thread`。\n"
"- 内存迁移需要 `migratepages`；否则仅跳过内存迁移。CPU 亲和性仍然适用，但性能可能会下降，因为现有页面不会移动到目标 NUMA 节点，并且可能通过更高延迟的远程 NUMA 访问读取。\n"
"- 如果异常从绑定流程中逃逸，`NPUWorker` 会记录一条警告并跳过该 rank 的 CPU 绑定。"
